quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,Indeed We sent it (Quran) down in the night of destiny (or the night of power)
  97,2,And do you know what the night of destiny is
  97,3,The night of destiny is better than a thousand months
  97,4,"The angels and the spirit came down in it, by their Master's permission, (with mandates) for every matter"
  97,5,It is peace (and well-being) until the rising of the dawn